{
  "_comment": "Canonical companion wire vocabulary. protocol.cjs (desktop) and CompanionProtocol.swift (iPhone) each hand-maintain these enums; protocolTables.test.cjs and CompanionProtocolTableTests.swift assert both sides equal THIS file, so any addition/rename on one platform breaks CI until the other is updated too.",
